{"id":768800349,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"10 months, 1 week","timestamp":1659996571,"status":15,"status_display":"Runtime Error","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/768800349/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"N/A","code":"class Solution {\n    public int romanToInt(String s) {\n        int sum = 0;\n        int[] arr = new int[s.length()];\n        for(int j = 0; j < s.length(); j++)\n            arr[j] =  convert(s.substring(j, j+1));\n        for(int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++)\n        {\n            \n            boolean adding = true;\n            int search = 1;\n            boolean notSmaller = true;\n            int pastCur = -1;\n            boolean pastAdd = true;\n            while(adding && i + search < s.length() && notSmaller)\n            {\n                if(arr[i+search] > arr[i])\n                    adding = false;\n                else if(arr[i+search+1] < arr[i])\n                    notSmaller = false;\n                else if(i != 0 && arr[i] == arr[i-1])\n                {\n                    adding = pastAdd;\n                    notSmaller = false;\n                }\n                    search++;\n            }\n            pastAdd = adding;\n            if(adding)\n                sum+= arr[i];\n            else\n                sum-= arr[i];\n        }\n        return(sum);\n    }\n    \n    public int convert(String s)\n    {\n        if(s.equals(\"M\"))\n            return(1000);\n        else if (s.equals(\"D\"))\n            return(500);\n        else if (s.equals(\"C\"))\n            return(100);\n        else if(s.equals(\"L\"))\n            return(50);\n        else if(s.equals(\"X\"))\n            return(10);\n        else if(s.equals(\"V\"))\n            return(5);\n        else \n            return(1);\n    }  \n    \n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer","has_notes":false}
